az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,2,6443623307,Bakcell,BAKCELL MMC,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/bakcell/id6443623307?uo=4,0.0,4.82735,80197,Lifestyle,"1. Məlumat səhifəsi – Mövcud balansınız və digər paketlərin həcmi ilə bağlı məlumatlar, xəttinizin və tarifinizin statusu
2. Tariflər – Özünüzə uyğun tarifi aktivləşdirmək, dəyişmək, deaktivasiya etmək imkanı və ətraflı məlumat hamısı bir arada
3. Sürətli internet və SMS paketləri – İstifadə tərzinizə uyğun paket seçmək imkanı
4. Bildirişlər – “Bakcell”in məhsulları, xidmətləri ilə bağlı ən son bildirişləri almaq, güzəştlərdən və kampaniyalardan hamıdan əvvəl faydalanmaq imkanı
5. Bir neçə nömrəyə nəzarət – Bir tətbiqdə bir neçə nömrəni qeydiyyatdan keçirmək, nəzarət və istifadə etmək imkanı
6. eSIM – Plastik SIM kartdan yeni nəsil eSIM nömrəyə keçmək imkanı
7. Balansın artırılması – Asanlıqla balansı artırmaq imkanı
8. CINKredit | KlassKredit – Balansda kifayət qədər vəsait olmayanda CINKredit yaxud KlassKredit vasitəsilə əlaqə saxlamaq imkanı
9. Rouminq – Xarici səfərlərdə daim ünsiyyətdə qalmaq üçün bütün imkanlar
10. Pulköçürmə – Öz balansınızdan digər CIN yaxud Klass abunəçisinin balansının artırmaq imkanı
11. Pulsuz SMS – Günlük 15 şəbəkədaxili və 10 şəbəkəxarici SMS pulsuz göndərmə imkanı
12. İstifadəçi səhifəsini tənzimləmək – Mobil tətbiqdə adınıza açdığınız hesabı rahatlıqla tənzimləmək imkanı
13. İstifadə tarixçəsi – İstifadə etdiyiniz mobil xidmətlər haqqında ümumi və ətraflı tarixçəni əldə etmək imkanı
14. Əməliyyatlar tarixçəsi – Mobil xidmətlər üçün etdiyiniz xərclərin tarixçəsini əldə etmək imkanı
15. “Mənə zəng et” xidməti – Balansınız bitsə belə, istənilən mobil nömrəyə sorğu göndərib, sizə zəng etməyi xahiş edə bilərsiniz
16. Xidmət mərkəzləri – Sizə yaxın olan xidmət mərkəzləri və rəsmi tərəfdaşlarımızın ünvanlarını anında görmək imkanı
17. STAR+ – Bonus kampaniyası. Mobil tətbiqdən istifadə və dostlarınızı tətbiqdən istifadəyə dəvət etməklə bonuslar toplamaq və hədiyyələrə dəyişmək imkanı
18. Dəyərləndirmə və bonus – Bizim tətbiqi dəyərləndirməklə bonus əldə etmək imkanı
19. Onlayn çat – “Bakcell”in rəqəmsal kanallar üzrə xidmət təmsilçiləri ilə ünsiyyət quraraq müraciətlərinizi birbaşa ünvanlamaq imkanı.
Qeydlər
- “Bakcell” tətbiqindən istifadə pulsuzdur, yalnız tətbiq daxilində xarici linklərə istinad və rouminqdə istifadə zamanı balansınızdan tarifinizə uyğun olaraq xidmət haqqı tutulacaq
- ""Qayda və Şərtləri"" qəbul etməklə siz abunəçi öhdəliklərinə məsul şəxs hesab olunursunuz.",2022-10-06T07:00:00Z,2025-11-12T07:51:26Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,3,6444889671,Nar+,Azerfon MMC,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/nar/id6444889671?uo=4,0.0,2.29538,325,Lifestyle,"""Nar+"" tətbiqimizi sizə təqdim edirik! Istifadəçi kabinetinizi idarə etmək üçün ən asan yol! Hesabınızı idarə etmək artıq bir toxunuş qədər asandır. Təkmilləşdirilmiş xüsusiyyətlər və sadələşdirilmiş naviqasiya ilə nəzarəti heç vaxt olmadığı kimi əlinizə götürün. İstər, qalıq istifadənin nəzarəti, istər, tənzimləmələrin idarə olunması və ya xüsusi imtiyazlara keçid imkanı, ehtiyacınız olan hər şeyi sizə təmin edirik. İndi yükləyin və hər zaman əlinizin altında olan rahatlığın bütün gücünü kəşf edin.

Tətbiq vasitəsi ilə nömrəndə müxtəlif tarifləri və paketləri müqaisə edə və sənə ən uyğununu seçib aktiv edə bilərsən. Paketlərin və xidmətlərin istifadə  müddətini, yenilənmə tarixini, statusunu daha rahat yoxlaya bilərsən. Artıq balansı artırmaq, kredit götürmək və balans köçürməsi etmək üçün şifrə yığmağa ehtiyac yoxdur. Nömrədən edilən zənglər, internet istifadəsi və bundan əlavə ümumi sərfiyyatı öyrənmək üçün Nar mərkəzinə yaxınlaşmadan tətbiq vasitəsi ilə məlumat ala bilərsən. Müxtəlif SİM kart əməliyyatları üçün sənə ən yaxın Nar satış və xidmət mərkəzinin ünvanını öyrənmək üçün sadəcə tətbiqə daxil olmaq kifayətdir. Əgər sualın yaranarsa, onlayn çat xidmətindən yararlana bilərsən.",2022-12-17T08:00:00Z,2025-11-20T21:26:19Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,4,547702041,Tinder Dating App: Meet & Date,Tinder LLC,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/tinder-dating-app-meet-date/id547702041?uo=4,0.0,4.78524,12940,Lifestyle,"MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.

With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:
Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.
HOW TINDER WORKS

It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.
PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:
– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!
TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like
EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone
UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, you can simply continue using Tinder for free.

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,6,1000744017,Namaz vaxti,Samir Shagavatov,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/namaz-vaxti/id1000744017?uo=4,0.0,4.44148,487,Lifestyle,"Namaz vaxtı proqramı Azərbaycanın şəhər və rayonları üçün namaz və oruc vaxtlarını göstərən proqramdır.

Proqram oflayn (offline) rejimdə işləyir, internet bağlantısına ehtiyac yoxdur. Həm namaz vaxtları, həm də ramazan təqvimi (oruc - imsak və iftar vaxtları) üçün istifadə oluna bilər. Azan vaxtı xəbərdarlıq etməsi üçün aşağıda ""Azan vaxtını bildirsin"" seçmək lazımdır. Paylaş düyməsi vasitəsilə proqramı facebook və digər sosial şəbəkələrdə paylaşa bilərsiniz.
DİQQƏT: Azanın işləməsi üçün proqramın bildiriş göndərməsinə (Notifications) icazə verilməlidir.
Vaxtlar qafqazislam.com (Qafqaz Müsəlmanları İdarəsinin rəsmi saytı) saytından götürülmüşdür.

İlk açılanda Bakı üçün bu günün namaz vaxtları görünür, yuxarı sol tərəfdə siyahıdan digər şəhər/rayonu seçə bilərsiniz. Tarixin solunda və sağında düymələri basmaqla dünən və sabah üçün namaz vaxtlarına baxa bilərsiniz.

Seçimlər bölməsində bildiriş səsi üçün müxtəlif azan və xəbərdarlıq səsi seçə bilərsiniz. Bundan əlavə 5 vaxtdan hansılarda azan bildirişi olmasını da seçə bilərsiniz. Əlavə olaraq imsak vaxtını göstərməsini seçimlərdə aktiv edə bilərsiniz.",2015-06-12T02:00:12Z,2025-09-01T15:28:06Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,11,351331194,Badoo: Dating app & Friends,Badoo Software Ltd,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/badoo-dating-app-friends/id351331194?uo=4,0.0,4.77517,2215,Lifestyle,"Boost your dating confidence with Badoo— the dating app that makes it easy to express your true self.

Plus, with our latest tech that aims to block fake, scam, and spam accounts, you can say hello to a fun and authentic dating experience.
Download Badoo to take your dating confidence to another level.""
Back yourself

Trust your experience

-Advanced Filters: Finesse your search, and save your time
-Profile Questions: Easily champion your personality

Go Premium

- And much more...

The price varies by country and may change without notice, but you can always see the exact price in the app. We will charge your card and your subscription will be automatically renewed unless you deactivate the automatic recharge a minimum of 24 hours before the end of your current subscription period. az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,12,6621272550,Alice AI,DIRECT CURSUS COMPUTER SYSTEMS TRADING LLC,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/alice-ai/id6621272550?uo=4,0.0,4.54167,24,Lifestyle,"Alice AI: texts, neural network, fresh ideas, knowledge, Russian-language AI chat.
Powerful Yandex AI on your phone helps with everyday chores and tackles tasks for study, work, and creativity.
Explore what the neural network can do with Alice—everything you expect from a smart chat in Russian.
Alice AI is Yandex’s family of generative models that power Alice. It includes:
- Alice AI LLM — a language model for answering questions and generating text
- Alice AI ART — an image model for creating visuals
- Alice AI VLM — a multimodal vision-language model for analyzing images, answering questions, and solving image-related tasks.
Ask questions, write and edit text—the Alice AI neural network responds accurately and comprehensively, and can enrich answers with images and source links. Speak by voice or type in chat.
Work with files (DOC, DOCX, PDF, TXT), structure information, and turn it into clear, usable reports. The Alice AI assistant quickly extracts key insights.

Work with photos—recognize text in images, identify objects, and get fast visual analysis. The AI chat assistant can pull data from a receipt photo, explain what’s in a shot, and convert it into an editable text format for further use.
Solve complex problems—reasoning mode produces not just quick and detailed answers, but thoughtful conclusions. You get well-founded solutions with expert-level analysis.
Create compelling English-language copy, ask questions, translate, and edit. Yandex Alice’s AI assistant helps draft anything—from personal emails and school assignments to business proposals.

Find inspiration: generate new project ideas, run brainstorms, craft descriptions and messages, and build your own text templates. Let Alice handle the routine. The AI assistant can write a letter, a script for an event or talk, suggest a post title, or even a name for your pet.
Create images and AI video—Yandex ART generates visuals or animates photos on request. Alice helps you produce striking social posts, a logo, or a birthday card.

Use AI chat for professional work. The assistant helps with programming and code, offering multiple solution approaches. Alice AI teaches logic, explains logical problems clearly, and shares interesting facts. Get advice and recommendations on any topic—Alice answers in detail, suggests step-by-step actions, and helps you plan.

Ask questions, type text, attach photos, videos, and files—or talk through the camera in real time with Live Mode. With the Pro option, show Alice what you see in Live Mode and get instant answers and ideas. Just open the Alice AI app and point your phone’s camera at whatever you want to learn about.

Alice AI can be your guide to landmarks, your kitchen co-pilot for “what can I cook with this?”, or your stylist for picking shoes to match your trousers. Ask anything and switch topics as needed. The neural network keeps context, recognizes objects in the frame, and delivers fast, in-depth answers.",2024-10-13T07:00:00Z,2025-11-01T08:52:32Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,14,6754551851,Deep Sea Fish Notes or Task,Komal Bahadur Bhandari,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/deep-sea-fish-notes-or-task/id6754551851?uo=4,0.0,0,0,Lifestyle,"Start from your Home Screen, where your nickname, profile icon, and level indicator reflect your progress. Each completed task, created note, or opened card adds to your achievements and brings you closer to the next level from Beginner to Master.
In the Diary, you can create your own cards with names, images, and notes. These cards are saved in your Gallery, joining twelve beautifully designed cards divided into four themed sections:
• Marine Fish Species learn about salmon, tuna, and halibut, the travelers and giants of the sea.
• Biology and Behavior explore feeding habits, reproduction, and migration patterns that shape ocean life.
• Fishing Methods discover how humans interact with marine nature through spinning, bottom gear, and nets.
• Seafood Recipes cook delicious dishes like lemon-baked tuna, herb salmon, or halibut with mashed potatoes.

Set your own Tasks and Goals, track them in the “In Progress” tab, and mark them as completed. Each finished goal boosts your stats and fills the Statistics Window, showing how many cards and tasks you’ve created.

In your Profile, personalize your journey edit your nickname, choose your avatar, adjust sound or music, and monitor your achievements. Earn points, level up, and see your rank rise with each discovery.

The ocean is vast, and learning never ends. With every note, every card, and every goal achieved, you navigate deeper into a world of knowledge, discipline, and curiosity. Explore, create, and master the sea one card at a time.",2025-11-01T07:00:00Z,2025-11-01T07:00:00Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,16,1462875428,Roborock,"Beijing Rockrobo Technology Co., Ltd.",https://apps.apple.com/az/app/roborock/id1462875428?uo=4,0.0,4.91737,2917,Lifestyle,"Roborock App is a dedicated application designed to control Roborock’s smart hardware devices.
It supports network-enabled products in Roborock’s robotic vacuum cleaners, wet and dry vacuum cleaners, and molecular sieve-based washer dryers.
You can remotely control smart devices and check their status and cleaning progress through this app anytime, anywhere.
Easily unlock more advanced features through the Roborock app.
【Roborock Robotic Vacuum Cleaner】
· Check the cleaning map and path anywhere and anytime you want, and control the cleaning progress in real-time.
· Choose from various personalized cleaning methods, including room cleaning, zone cleaning, scheduled cleaning, and spot cleaning routines.
· Set up frequently used cleaning tasks as routines for one-tap starts.
· Choose multiple cleaning preferences, including Vacuum, Mop, Vac & Mop, SmartPlan (applicable to certain models only), and Customize mode.
· Set up a personalized cleaning plan by adjusting suction power, water flow, cleaning frequency, and route (applicable to certain models only).
· Enables you to edit a map based on your home and set names for thresholds, carpets, floor types, furniture, and rooms.
· Set up invisible walls and no-go zones and your robot will not cross or enter them during cleaning.
· Enjoy a variety of fun features, including remote viewing, obstacle photos, pet snapshots, cruise mode, pet search, and custom tones (applicable to select models only).
【Roborock Wet and Dry Vacuum Cleaner】
· Adjust water flow, suction power, roller speed, and detergent level (applicable to select models only) based on the floor and dirt level.
· Smart scheduled self-cleaning and drying: automatically initiates self-cleaning and drying based on historical operation records.
【Roborock Washer Dryer】
· Check the washing progress and operating status anywhere and anytime you want.
· Choose from over 20 smart washing and drying programs to meet the professional needs of various fabrics and clothing, ensuring optimal washing performance.
· Set one program as the App Program for quick access on the control panel.
【Permissions】

To provide certain services, you need to enable the relevant permissions on your mobile device. We will only need the relevant permissions and access your personal information (if relevant) when you use the relevant functions. For the optional permissions, you can refuse or withdraw these permissions at any time, for which you may not be able to use the corresponding services, but this will not affect other functions of the App. The current permissions that the app may need are as follows:
· Location (Optional)
Accesses location information to connect to WiFi, find nearby devices ready for connection, and retrieve details about the current WiFi connection.
· Camera (Optional)
Enables the camera to scan QR codes for easier WiFi connection.
· Photos (Optional)

Allows access to photos for uploading profile pictures and attaching images when providing feedback. If your device supports features like downloading obstacle images, taking screenshots, or recording during remote viewing, photos and videos can be stored.
· Microphone (Optional)
Used for sound transmission on devices that support remote viewing.
· WLAN (Optional)
Facilitates connection to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices for communication and connectivity.
· Bluetooth (Optional)
Enables connection to Bluetooth signals from smart devices for communication and device connecting.
· Notifications (Optional)
Allows the app to send you device and system notifications.
· Local Network (Optional)
When connecting devices on the iOS local network, grants access to the local network to connect to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices.
· Siri & Search (Optional)
When opening Siri on iOS, interacts with Siri to control the starting and moving of devices based on the Routines set up in the mobile device.",2019-06-18T06:57:57Z,2025-11-19T09:35:50Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,18,6502763303,iVolt,"ITICKET, MMC",https://apps.apple.com/az/app/ivolt/id6502763303?uo=4,0.0,5,10,Lifestyle,"iVolt is a pioneering electric vehicle (EV) charging solutions provider based in Azerbaijan, dedicated to accelerating the adoption of electric vehicles through innovative and accessible charging infrastructure. Established in March 2024, iVolt has quickly positioned itself as a key player in the EV ecosystem, focusing on delivering seamless and efficient charging services to both individual and corporate clients.\n
Our Vision and Mission

Vision: To become the leading provider of electric vehicle charging solutions in Azerbaijan and expand our reach globally, driving the transition towards sustainable transportation. Mission: To provide reliable, efficient, and accessible EV charging solutions, fostering the widespread adoption of electric vehicles and contributing to a cleaner, greener future. Core Business Directions
iVolt operates across three main business directions:
iVolt App (Platform):

B2C and B2B Payments and Reporting: The iVolt app serves as a comprehensive platform for managing payments and generating detailed reports for both individual EV owners and corporate clients. It ensures a smooth and user-friendly experience, simplifying the process of finding and using charging stations. Operator of Charging Stations:

Nationwide Infrastructure: iVolt owns and operates a network of charging stations across Azerbaijan. These stations are strategically located to maximize accessibility and convenience for EV drivers, ensuring they can charge their vehicles whenever and wherever needed.

Operational Excellence: Beyond installation, iVolt takes on the role of an operator, managing the day-to-day operations, monitoring station performance, and providing 24/7 customer support to ensure optimal service delivery and user satisfaction.
Services to Third-Party Charging Station Owners:

Platform Integration: iVolt offers integration services to third-party charging station owners, allowing them to leverage the iVolt platform for enhanced functionality and user engagement. Installation and Servicing: iVolt provides comprehensive installation and maintenance services, ensuring that all charging stations are operating at peak efficiency and reliability. Innovative Partnership Models
iVolt has developed flexible partnership models to cater to the diverse needs of its business clients:

App Only Model: Partners can use the iVolt app for managing their existing charging stations, benefiting from scalable usage fees and performance-based discounts. Ownership and Profit Sharing Models: iVolt collaborates with partners by providing and installing infrastructure, with revenue-sharing agreements tailored to ensure mutual growth and profitability. Corporate and Retail Client Solutions

B2C Retail Clients: Individual EV owners can easily locate, reserve, and pay for charging services through the iVolt app, enjoying a hassle-free charging experience. B2B Corporate Clients: Large EV fleets and taxi companies receive preferential rates and dedicated services, optimizing their operations and reducing costs. Commitment to Sustainability

At iVolt, sustainability is at the core of everything we do. By promoting the use of electric vehicles and expanding the charging infrastructure, we aim to reduce carbon emissions and support a greener, more sustainable environment for future generations.
Conclusion

As a forward-thinking company, iVolt is committed to innovation, excellence, and sustainability in the EV charging industry. With our robust platform, extensive network, and customer-centric approach, we are poised to lead the way in transforming transportation and driving the future of electric mobility.
For more information, visit our website at www.ivolt.az.",2024-06-20T07:00:00Z,2025-10-28T17:43:45Z

az,Azerbaijan,Lifestyle,6012,21,1582810683,Дом с Алисой,DIRECT CURSUS COMPUTER SYSTEMS TRADING LLC,https://apps.apple.com/az/app/%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%BC-%D1%81-%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%B9/id1582810683?uo=4,0.0,4.90308,227,Lifestyle,"Дом с Алисой — приложение, в котором удобно настраивать умный дом и управлять им даже в дороге. Подключайте лампочки, пылесосы, датчики и тысячи других устройств — и контролируйте их здесь или через колонку.
• ВСЁ В ОДНОМ ПРИЛОЖЕНИИ
Добавляйте и удаляйте самые разные устройства, от колонок с Алисой до кондиционеров, меняйте названия и расположение — и настраивайте, как вам нравится.
• УДАЛЁННОЕ УПРАВЛЕНИЕ
Дом под контролем, даже если вы далеко: скажем, по дороге на дачу можно заранее включить обогреватель.
• ОДНА КОМАНДА ДЛЯ ВСЕГО
Запускайте нескольких устройств одной фразой — например, «Алиса, скоро буду дома». Настройте сценарий, и по этой команде включится кондиционер, пылесос начнёт уборку, а в коридоре зажжётся свет.
• ДОМ, КОТОРЫЙ САМ О ВАС ЗАБОТИТСЯ

Подключайте датчики — к примеру, температуры и влажности, — и проверяйте, как дела дома. Создайте сценарий, добавьте обогреватель и что-нибудь ещё — и дом будет сам следить, чтобы в нём хорошо дышалось.
• РУТИННЫЕ ДЕЛА ПО РАСПИСАНИЮ
Поручите часть домашних дел Алисе. Достаточно один раз настроить расписание, и она будет сама поливать цветы и включать перед сном увлажнитель.
• СЦЕНАРИЙ В ОДНО КАСАНИЕ
Добавьте сценарий в виджет — и кнопка управления будет всегда под рукой, на главном экране телефона.
• ТЫСЯЧИ РАЗНЫХ УСТРОЙСТВ
Подключайте сколько угодно домашних приборов разных производителей: в магазине вы узнаете эти устройства по отметке «Работает с Алисой».",2022-05-23T07:00:00Z,2025-11-13T06:42:33Z
